d = {'hours': 789, 'minutes': 12, 'seconds': 34}
s = '%(hours)s:%(minutes)s:%(seconds)s' % d
if with_fsp:
    d['microseconds'] = 511581
    s += '.%(microseconds)s' % d
expected = datetime.timedelta(**d)
if with_negate:
    expected = -expected
    s = '-' + s
tdelta = converters.convert_timedelta(s)
self.assertEqual(tdelta, expected)
